Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During our visit to Okayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We took on the quest of investigating the identity\Nof a woman we met there who lost her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clues provided to us were her eight sketches.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amid our investigation, maybe unsurprisingly, we came across\Nher friend Nonomiya Kanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who had been looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:27.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Based on Kanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s Intel, we learned\Nthat her name is Kichise Mayuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kichise Mayuko (25)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:33.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} happened to be the witness who could prove the\Ninnocence of Kanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s brother, currently arrested for robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nonomiya Keigo (28)\NKanae's Elder Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} cannot retrieve her\Nmemory, his name will not be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we continued on our search...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room was disarranged\Nand a suspicious shadow was following us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Triggered a fishy y feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} suddenly went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad, at this rate Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like fog clearing up in a swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see through both romance and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lost memory will be restored...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the conclusion of the Okayama-Kurashiki tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.59,Signs,,0,0,0,,Washuzan Observation Deck
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we'd better inform the police and petition for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, they're the police who treated my\Ninnocent brother as if he were the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just can't bring myself to trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I request that we continue like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mayuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my brother will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this only for your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just feel ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I was struggling to recall my past,\Nfeeling down and helpless in tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That past back came to haunt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is somewhat mortifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Definitely want to recall my true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How admirable, that Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that she's actually a strong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you came to visit a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A coincidence again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fate is a curious thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:38.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,Taira Kenzou (40)\NPatissier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,However, I am shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,To the she'd lost her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can do to help, ask away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've met him somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because that man is like a god among local confectionery fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've also done a report on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this person Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:12.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nashida Teruyuki (35)\NTown Magazine Reporter\NFormer Sommelier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks completely different now, so I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We only have five more sketches to check out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what places these point to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still can't wrap my head around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just hit me, but could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Referring to the boiling pot reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boiling... pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A boiling pot reading is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:42.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A ritual in this Kibitsu Shrine that's been\Npassed down from ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kibitsu Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:46.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,By drawing upon the loudness and length\Nof the sound of rice boiling in a pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good or bad omens are predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your memory has returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize this lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did I cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has she requested a boiling pot reading before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the day before the robbery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to turn over a new leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Discarding my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's high time that I got back on my two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you were walking around Okayama where you were\Nborn and raised because you wanted to re-envision yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just found out the reason why you were\Nvisiting the places depicted in your sketches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More comments are posted on our website!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People witnessed her in Kurashiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We immediately journeyed to Kurashiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Ohashi House
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a match to that window grill?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it actually meant the Kurashiki grillwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurashiki grillwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a characteristic design in Kurashiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll see a lot of it once we go to the Bikan historical area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,aesthetic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bikan historical area?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:17.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kurashiki Bikan Historical Area
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure seems to me that Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just someone asking for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young boy, give this a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:54.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,Handmade Sparrow-Shaped Pancake Workshop
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, smile at the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:08.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kurashiki Ivy Square
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:09.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thereafter, we discovered subsequent locations\Ncorresponding with the sketches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:11.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kurabo Memorial Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s memory was also recovering little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Came here before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:31.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ohara Museum of Art
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yurinso Villa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thus we were down to two sketches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Momotaro Museum of Illusions
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hint to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spinning this disk will{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge the number of demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The grapes vanished and the bananas become two bundles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They painted a picture of grapes on the face-up\Nsurfaces of this accordion-shaped object...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on the surfaces facing down, they painted bananas instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the mirror below that object.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will reflect the bananas that are drawn on the downward surfaces?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Changing the angle makes you see\Ndifferent things—how interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Changing the angle makes you see different things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,♪ Waiting for the person who...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,♪ Never came in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moon anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,Osanai Finance, Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan Episode 641\NFansub Release by DCTP\NRipped by DJ VK & Innushka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you've recovered your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you recalled where the jewelry is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You reveal your intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I who wrote that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mayuko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is already back in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not the sister of Nonomiya Keigo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}—suspect\Nof the jewelry robbery—am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be apparent to us if we just think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the event that the suspect denies charges...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relative visits are almost prohibited except for attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, during my visit at the police station...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My big brother firmly said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already seen through your true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a loan contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishida Kanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's just like you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why she posed as his sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was not to clear Nonomiya's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your purpose was the jewelry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've known that you'd get caught\Nposing as his sister once we investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It shows how tight of a corner she was driven into.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to her debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some trashy man hoodwinked me into\Ngetting loans to support him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the finance company turned out to be a loan shark to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night before yesterday, I went to Mayuko's\Napartment with the intent to borrow money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the jewelry!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, I didn't quite understand what happened in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But soon as I got wind of the jewelry robbery via the\Nnews next morning, everything became clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The statement given out by Nonomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\NI saw on the news was not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man conked Nonomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and made him a scapegoat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the woman he claimed to have seen was in fact Mayuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, aside from the witness being Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything you said was announced in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to the two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I gathered that Mayuko had betrayed the\Nman and hidden the jewelry somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I played my cards right, I might even be able to get out of debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that in mind, I hurriedly tried to locate Mayuko's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, just as I found Mayuko, her memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suddenly didn't know what to do at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, President Osanai from\Nthe loan company came to collect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And I inadvertently told him about the stolen jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:08.62,Signs,,0,0,0,,Osanai Norio (38)\NPresident of Osanai Finance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He coerced you into posing as Nonomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nsister and getting in contract with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All for the purpose of drawing out the whereabouts of\Nthe jewelry once Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} regained her memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to usurp them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, please hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you ave a call from the Okayama police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must've taken the man into custody\Nfrom the license plate Conan reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying I'm the jewelry robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only planning to con her out of the jewelry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because my company is in dire fiscal straits...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:15:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He admitted that he was responsible for\Ngrabbing Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the Bikan area...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But denied having done anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's definitely just trying to talk his way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The attacker at the observation deck\Nmust've been that Osanai guy as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I beg to differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember any characteristics of the man who\Nattacked Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the observation deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man was left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Osanai is right-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, there were actually two people stalking Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them is the right-handed man who was\Nworking with Kanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and following us -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The finance company president, Osanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the remaining left-handed man would be the jewelry robber...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So who was this man responsible for attacking\NMayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the observation deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right now you should swiftly cut the Gordian Knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hint to our culprit was portrayed in\NMayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s sketches from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look at the last sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture of grapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying this hints to our culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Nashida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you're a former sommelier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, a sommelier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wears a badge in the shape of grapes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in the picture that was torn\Noff in Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had something shiny on his chest, was it a sommelier badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, immediately before Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nattacked at the observation deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apologies, but the editor-in-chief called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will be back in about an hour, so please go ahead and dine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took off somewhere, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you suspecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man at the observation deck got conked by\NConan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} with a can and injured his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nashida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, why did you suddenly decide to wear a hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to insinuate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm hiding any wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Nashida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sketch was in fact showing something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-neechan, the picture of grapes didn't\Nmean a sommelier badge, but this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to look this way, right Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s muscat parfait?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's akin to that mirror trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Changing the angle makes you see different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, it's likely that Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan witnessed the moment when Nashida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were shaking hands at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why Nashida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} extended his left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because he already knew Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was left-handed, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man from that time was also left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time for you to show yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know you've been eavesdropping on us over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm too broke to open a new shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since I gambled away my old shop\NI couldn't get any loans from any banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I recruited Mayuko and committed the robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was an accomplice to the robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would imagine she was the lookout or the getaway driver, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you guessed right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I was witnessed by that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, you beat Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to her apartment and dragged her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tried to get the jewelry back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But caused Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to fall down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were then surprised by Kanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s scream and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, you learned about Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Namnesia from the town magazine website...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition to the fact that I was investigating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then destroyed any evidence in Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nroom showing the relationship between you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And attempted to get in touch with us in a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All for the purpose of getting the jewelry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went missing from the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, your memory has already returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you mumbled this at the Bikan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you were reminded of the\Nnight scene you saw there in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times have I tried to pull myself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, each time the person I trusted would betray me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fell love with Taira and he bid me to co-own a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought this was my{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce, that very\Nsame Taira compelled me to rob the jewelry store!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I can never regain my footing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Defiantly, I thought I should just keep all the loot to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not turn even more evil for the heck of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not fall deeper for all I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After seeing the boiling pot ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You requested a fortune reading with the\Nintention of discarding your past and start afresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you've regained your memory, you\Nshould be able to recall that feeling of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran said something about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How admirable, that Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that she's actually a strong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe she's now praying for you to straighten\Nyourself out this time with that strength of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next day, thanks to the testimony\Nof the now-arrested Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonomiya Keigo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was proven to be innocent and was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Octopus rice and.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to be late for the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My octopus rice and beeeeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:00.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cold, I have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.55,0:24:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys I don't know suddenly came to my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't behave, Daddy's gonna get angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a wolf-crier he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, despite the wolf-crier telling the truth in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.49,0:24:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was eaten by the wolf because no one believed him, right?
